column5: Perhaps he didn't get his morning coffee. Betcha that woke him up. ouch!
Ouch !! I could feel that all the way over here:stretcher:
Ouch, well at least he and the bike did not both go in the drink!
/me clinching my jaw....  Opps not IRC...  /me clinching my testicles....  Opps darn not IRC...  /quit
that's why they call them donorcycles.
It looked intentional!  I used to believe in evolution, but now I'm not so sure!!
looks like he cut the corner to much and the side compartment caught the stubby post.
Yes, I can see that now. This time I viewed it with the sound on and I could hear the hit against the bollard. Oh well, I guess I still believe in evolution!!
